10. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person watching drama movies##2
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
13. the person playing scrabble is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
