.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, lacrosse, tennis
House: farmhouse, craftsman, tower, ranch-style
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the craftsman house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the ranch-style house##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the tower house is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the craftsman house is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee   | water     | mirinda    | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| Sport         | climbing | lacrosse  | tennis     | cycling  |
| House     | farmhouse     | tower | ranch-style | craftsman     |

